===Format===
* '''Pre-Quarter Finals:''''' November 20th - 23rd, 2024
** 64 teams, 4 matchdays.
*** 32 invited teams.
*** 32 from Open Qualifiers.
** Teams are divided equally into 4 groups of 16.
** Each group will play 24 matches in 4 days.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams from each group}} advance to Group Stage.
** {{bgcolortext|down|Bottom 8 teams from each group}} are eliminated.

* '''Group Stage:''''' November 24th - 27th, 2024
** 32 teams
** Teams are divided equally into 2 groups of 16.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams from each group}} advance to Upper Bracket.
** {{bgcolortext|stayup|Bottom 8 teams from each group}} advance to Lower Bracket.

* '''Lower Bracket:''''' May 4th - 5th & 9th, 2025
** 16 teams
** 18 matches, 3 matchdays.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} advance to Last Chance Qualifiers.
** {{bgcolortext|down|Bottom 8 teams}} are eliminated.

* '''Upper Bracket:''''' May 6th - May 9th, 2025
** 16 teams
** 24 matches, 4 matchdays.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} advance to Grand Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|stayup|Bottom 8 teams}} advance to Last Chance Qualifiers.

* '''Last Chance Qualifiers:''''' May 10th - 13th, 2025
** 16 teams
*** {{bgcolortext|stayup|8 teams}} from Upper Bracket.
*** {{bgcolortext|stayup|8 teams}} from Lower Bracket.
** 24 matches, 4 matchdays.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} advance to Grand Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|down|Bottom 8 teams}} are eliminated.

* '''Sky Surge''''' May 15th, 2025
** 16 teams
*** {{bgcolortext|stayup|8 teams}} from Upper Bracket.
*** {{bgcolortext|stayup|8 teams}} from Last Chance Qualifiers.
** Teams will play 6 matches on the first day and on the basis of overall standing teams will get bonus points.
